{"tid":1966502,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"最近尼班直銷/傳銷師冇得企街，竟然直接搵上門都有嘅","createTime":"2020-04-10T08:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T20:10:32.000Z","uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7714b918c9b07e75f2c539bed4cbb9eae61d35a3","tid":1966502,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T08:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec542ade2972ea3ed0cf54e5ea1dcbb50d465f04","tid":1966502,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"南B記得唔好亂跟人地去陌生地方"},{"pid":"bd61757080f1981c61e2a43fbf7767f8c5a5ccc1","tid":1966502,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T20:08:28.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span style=\"color: green;\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi64429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=849bffbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi64429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7799393f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi64429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7ecbf507\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b68c79dbd82b34a3f46ecc1feb44850a1bdd6a09","tid":1966502,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T20:09:08.000Z","msg":"傳銷公司(KJ Team) 經歷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=4cibbb6e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D4cibbb6e&d=GkP5J4C4AUyWsqXHyTPi64429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=7c35f022\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=4cibbb6e</a><br />\n<br />\n事主係該公司遇上本post 提過的 Hugo Wong 與 Cherry<br />\n<br />\n###############################################<br />\n<br />\n姓名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n電話: 59920798<br />\n電話: 51610763 (可以 iMessage)<br />\n最新IG: yyyyy_1ii (原名:totor.00 )<br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院<br />\n<br />\n更多資料及圖片:<b